snippet.title: CORSAIRS LEGACY Gameplay Update Trailer (2022) 4K
snippet.description:
Corsairs Legacy Official Gameplay Update Trailer New for PC in remastered/upscaled 4K ULTRA HD and improved to smooth 60 FPS.

Release Date: 2022

Pirate open-world RPG awaits you! You’re going to experience sea battles, island exploration, and convoluted intrigues. Dive into a life full of battles and let it take you on countless adventures! The game is being developed by Mauris.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1594880/Corsairs_Legacy__Pirate_Action_RPG/

Like and subscribe for more and best game videos every day!
